name: Doggo
description: Dogecoin founder BillyM2k tweeted a video of Doggo and this project was launched on pump.fun. I saw the potential that this could bring to the crypto space and its easy onboarding opportunities for Solana. I have since taken over the project, since it was the first launched in regards to the tweet. We plan on working with some of the notable Solana companies in the space, including Hellomoon, to bring somthing unique to the space.
